title: Singularity
lyrics: Tone mueonga kkaejineun sori nan mundeuk jameseo kkae najseoleum gadeukhan sori guireul maka bojiman jamel deulji mothae moki jakku apawa gamssa boryeohajima naegen moksoriga eopseo oneuldo geu soril dureo tto olligoisseo geu soriga ieoreo buteun hosue tto geumi ga gu hosue naega nal beoryeottjana nae moksoril neol wihae mudeottjana nal beorin gyeoul hosu wiro dukkeoun eoleumi eoreottne jamsi deureogan kkum sokedo nareul gwirophineun hwansang tongeun yeojeonhe naneun nal ireun geolkka anim neol ireun geolkka na mundeuk hosuro daryeoga ogeu soke nae eolgulisseo butakhae amu maldohajima ipeul makuryeo soneul ppeodeo bojiman gyeolkugen eonjega bomiwa eoleumdeuleun noka naeryeo holleo ga Tell me nae moksoriga gajjaramyeon nal beoriji malasseoyahaettneunji Tell me gotongjacha gajjaramyeon gu tae naega mueolhaeyahaettneunji
